                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols. 3r-95v)&#xD;
I–1) Homily by Timothy (Damātewos) of Alexandria for the 12th day of Ḫǝdār (fols. 3ra-9ra l.3); two miracles (fols. 9ra l.4-10rb l.1); commemorative notice (fols. 10rb l.2-11vb l.18) &#xD;
I–2) Anonymous homily for the 12th day of Tāḫśāś (fols. 11vb l.19-16vb); miracle (fol. 17ra-vb l.5); commemorative notice (fols. 17vb l.6-18va l.3) &#xD;
I–3) Anonymous homily for the 12th day of Ṭǝrr (fols. 18va l.4-27ra l.5); miracle (fols. 27ra l.6-28vb l.17); commemorative notice (fols. 27vb l.18-28ra l.11) &#xD;
I–4) Anonymous homily for the 12th day of Yakkātit (fols. 28ra l.12-31ra l.13); miracle (fols. 31ra l.14-32ra l.2); commemorative notice (fol. 32ra l.3-vb l.2) &#xD;
I–5) Homily by Patriarch John of Antiochia for the 12th day of Maggābit (fols. 32vb l.3-46rb l.17); miracle (fols. 46rb l.18-49vb l.2); commemorative notice (fols. 49vb l.3-50ra l.8) &#xD;
I–6) [Homily by John the Orthodox for the 12th of Miyāzyā] (fols. 50ra l.9-54rb), miracle (fols. 54va-56vb l.5); commemorative notice (fols. 56vb l.6-57rb l.5) &#xD;
I–7) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Ethiopia for the 12th of Gǝnbot (fols. 57rb l.6-59ra l.5); miracle (fols. 59ra l.6-61ra l.12); commemorative notice (fol. 61ra l.13-vb l.10) &#xD;
I–8) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Aksum for the 12th day of Sane (fols. 61vb l.11-74va l.11); miracle (fol. 74va l.4-vb l.2); commemorative notice (fols. 74vb l.3-76ra l.2) &#xD;
I–9) Homily of Bishop John for the 12th day of Ḥamle (fols. 76ra l.3-80ra l.3); miracle (fol. 80ra l.3-vb l.8); commemorative notice (fols. 80vb l.9-81rb l.15) &#xD;
I–10) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th day of Naḥāse (fols. 81rb l.16-84ra l.13); miracle (fol. 84ra l.14-vb l.12); commemorative notice (fols. 84vb l.13-85ra l.1) &#xD;
I–11) Anonymous homily for the 12th day of Maskaram (fols. 85ra l.1-87va l.14); miracle (fols. 87va l.15-89va l.14); commemorative notice (fol. 89va l.15-vb) &#xD;
I–12) Anonymous homily for the 12th day of Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 90ra-93rb l.5); miracle (fols. 93rb l.6-94vb l.9); commemorative notice (fols. 94vb l.10-95vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
