                        <seg type="script">Mediocre, rather careless</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, red (vivid crimson).</seg>
                        <date>First half of the 19th century</date>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the donor and his family members (the whole name or the second component); 1st, 2nd, 5th 6th, 17th and 18th line on the incipit page; two initial lines of the sub-sections; names of the months on fols. 76r, 81rb; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of the chapter dividers (e.g., fol. 32va); elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
